          fr.cyann.react.ListVar<V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<V>, java.util.Collection<V>, java.util.List<V>
public class ListVar<V>
extends Var<java.util.List<V>>
implements java.util.List<V>

The ListVar class. Creation date: 12 oct. 2013. Emit signal when list changed.
In case of List type, emit also when any contained value in the list change.
Based on decorator design pattern from GoF.

Version:
v0.1
Author:
Yann Caron
